## What This License Covers

This CC BY 4.0 license covers all files in this repository:

### Mathematical Kernel
| File | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `butterflyfx/kernel.py` | HelixKernel state machine |
| `butterflyfx/manifold.py` | GenerativeManifold mathematical surfaces |
| `butterflyfx/substrate.py` | ManifoldSubstrate token model |
| `butterflyfx/primitives.py` | Fundamental dimensional types |
| `butterflyfx/graphics3d.py` | Pure 3D mathematics |

### Foundation & Utilities
| File | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `butterflyfx/foundation.py` | HelixDB, HelixFS, HelixStore, HelixGraph |
| `butterflyfx/utilities.py` | HelixPath, HelixQuery, HelixCache, HelixSerializer |

### Networking Layer
| File | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `butterflyfx/transport.py` | Helix network transport protocol |
| `butterflyfx/audio_transport.py` | Real-time audio transport |
| `butterflyfx/manifold_server.py` | Math transmission server |

### Documentation
| File | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `docs/BUTTERFLYFX_WHITE_PAPER.md` | Conceptual introduction |
| `docs/BUTTERFLYFX_FORMAL_KERNEL.md` | Mathematical model and proofs |
| `docs/BUTTERFLYFX_SPECIFICATION.md` | Formal language-agnostic specification |

